headline: Analysts say Dexcom’s FDA warning unlikely to impact 2025 revenue
summary: Dexcom was issued with an FDA warning letter after issues with “manufacturing processes and quality management systems.”

headline: Patient Monitoring Stocks Q4 Results: Benchmarking ResMed (NYSE:RMD)
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how ResMed (NYSE:RMD) and the rest of the patient monitoring stocks fared in Q4.
